{
  "stem": "22959.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when it-- and they had them-- shop, the workshop, out of the ghetto-- outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when it happened, when they had the action, when they surrounded our ghetto, and when they liquidate the ghetto, he took his whole family to the shop.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was hiding there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it didn't work out because the Germans found the shop, and they killed everybody there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he felt that by having the Schein, he will be able to survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] do you want me to describe you a little bit the action at the end when they liquidated the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do, but if you want to tell us more about ghetto life-- how long you were there, and what it was like for you, individually?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For me individually, I was so young.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked-- OK, I worked-- I worked for the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I worked for the Russians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was afraid, in a way, to find work in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the Germans-- because I was afraid that somebody will tell them that I was working for, for the-- for the Soviets, for the Russians.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What were you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was working in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means-- that means-- that means financial department as, as an office worker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not much, not much, because I was young, and I couldn't-- I didn't know it that well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was working-- employed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why, maybe that was just my imagination.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe it wouldn't even happen anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I wasn't exactly anxious to find a job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- but people, people who were in the ghetto, they found little jobs.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
